  /* ============================================================================
     ===== Phase 9.1.51 — Vendor catalog tables ================================
     ============================================================================
     Three flexible-schema catalogs sitting under the Vendors page as sub-tabs.
     Each table has a `columns` array defining its schema and a `rows` array
     holding the data. Columns can be added/renamed/deleted by the user; types
     are: text | number | yesno | tags | image | url.

     Built-in columns are marked `builtin: true` so the UI shows a small lock
     icon on the delete affordance (still editable, just communicates that the
     column has special meaning).
     ============================================================================ */

